text: Adiba Anjum Mita is a Bangladeshi politician who is elected as Member of 11th Jatiya Sangsad of Reserved Seats for Women. She is a politician of Bangladesh Awami League. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:People from Rajshahi District Category:11th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Women members of the Jatiya Sangsad Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people
